caption: WOW! I received  a courteous friendly greeting upon entering. My sandwich was made to perfection and the salad, they followed my directions precisely. I must add that the manager made my lunch experience quite pleasurable I will be returning soon and very soon. Thanks Amoi  for best customer service ever.

dinner tonight was Great! Chicken Kabobs were the best-very tender. Hummas was really good, not so much garlic like most places. Hubby had the lamb chops, very tender and good. Order and pay at the counter, they bring it to you.  Bakery and Bar there too. The wraps looked good, next time. Looks like enough to share! Will go back for sure.

The original chicken was crispy, tender and juicy. The coleslaw and pickles were a perfect match for the chicken burger. In contrast, the spicy chicken was salty. The loaded fries and regular fries were nicely seasoned. I loved them.

Delicious sandwich! I tried Potbelly for the first time today and it's officially one of the highlights of my day! I had the chicken salad which comes with provolone and had them add bacon. They toast the bread and cheese first, and then they add the meat and condiments, which equals a very well balanced temperature. The chicken salad mixture is very tasty and not too dry or over dressed with mayo, and the roll is a perfect size, and it's narrow, which made it easy to handle while I ate. A new favorite for sure!

This place is partially hidden by construction scaffolding at the moment but it's worth finding. The food is good, fresh, made as you watch, and surprisingly it's not overpriced.  Pro tip: use their app to pay. It won't save you money immediately but you'll start getting free stuff pretty quickly. My lunch yesterday (late Feb, 2018) was free because of a promotion for a new sandwich. (This review has nothing to do with the freebie - I eat there a couple of times a month.)  Even better they email you several days in advance of those deals, unlike other places where you get an hour or two of notice or you have to hunt through their app or website.  Best of all the staff are some of the friendliest people in the area. Chat with them a bit and I bet you'll walk out with a smile on your face to match your full belly.

Best part about this place though is the AMAZING Cookies!!... All are good but THE BEST one is the Chocolate Brownie cookie!! Better than most cookies from dedicated bake shops! Grab a couple and thank me later!
